Orbeetle (TCG)

Orbeetle has been featured on 7 different cards since it debuted in the Sword & Shield expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Orbeetle cards are normally Grass-type or Psychic-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Orbeetle
